item.description:
Come and celebrate Australia Day with a night of Australian Trivia and live music from "The Beantown Project" at Tommy Doyle's Irish Pub, Harvard Square. There will be prizes galore, meat pies, music, dancing and much more...

When: Friday, January 26, 7:00pm (trivia game to start at 7:30pm)

Where: Tommy Doyle's Irish Pub, 96 Winthrop Street, Harvard Square, Cambridge

Cost: $20 per person, Pay at the Door

Host: American Australian Association

group.name: The Boston Expat Aussie Meetup Group

item.name: Aussie Day "Trivia Night"
